works well, and has a fantastic battery life. However, I am giving it 3 stars because it offers 100GB Google Drive storage with purchase, but this is not the case. It says an offer will be sent to you upon purchase. I never received an offer. I sent a message to Google Drive, but never received a response. I bought the chromebook to replace my main laptop. Cloud storage is vital on a chromebook, and not receiving my 2 year storage is very upsetting.</span></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-top-small review-comments comments-for-R21DGVZ1VHNGLP"><div data-reftag="cm_cr_arp_d_cmt_opn" aria-live="polite" data-a-expander-name="review_comment_expander" class="a-row a-expander-container a-expander-inline-container"><a href="javascript:void(0)" data-action="a-expander-toggle" class="a-expander-header a-declarative a-expander-inline-header a-link-expander" data-a-expander-toggle="{&quot;allowLinkDefault&quot;:true, &quot;expand_prompt&quot;:&quot;&quot;, &quot;collapse_prompt&quot;:&quot;&quot;}"><i class="a-icon a-icon-expand"></i><span class="a-expander-prompt"><span class="review-comment-total aok-hidden">2</span><span class="a-size-base">2 comments</span></span></a><span class="a-letter-space"></span><i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" aria-label="|"><span class="a-icon-alt">|</span></i><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span data-hook="review-voting-widget" class="a-size-base cr-vote"><span class="cr-vote-buttons"><span class="a-color-secondary">Was this review helpful to you?</span><span class="a-letter-space"></span><span class="a-button a-button-beside-text a-button-small cr-vote-button cr-vote-yes" id="a-autoid-20"><span class="a-button-inner"><a href="https://www.amazon.com/ap/signin?openid.return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FASUS-C201-11-6-Chromebook-Rockchip%2Fproduct-reviews%2FB00VUV0MG0%2Fref%3Dcm_cr_arp_d_vote_lft%3Fie%3DUTF8%26voteInstanceId%3DR21DGVZ1VHNGLP%26voteValue%3D1%26csrfT%3DgCRS7JqxE1AbeQszB4FXpLjH2aTgAQu7OmwqFxAAAAAJAAAAAFgCDjpyYXcAAAAA%2